**Issue**: Export buttons not working  
**Solution**: Ensure JavaScript is enabled and library files are loaded correctly.

**Issue**: Risk calculations seem incorrect  
**Solution**: Run [validateRiskCalculations()](file:///c:/Users/NV/.gemini/antigravity/playground/galactic-kepler/js/app.js#266-268) in browser console to verify calculation engine.

